OOC: Ah, cool. I had forgottont hat you had named him already. The discription just made me think of Skywarp.

Super Cyclonus <supercyclonus@...> wrote:          
--- Richard Allen <roborick007@...> wrote:

> OOC: Preston, do we have ourselves Skywarp rebuilt in a Armada
> Starscream like body?

OOC: I did not intend to, but its open. He is Nightrazor, the minion
created by Cyclonus from the soldiers found in a decepticon shuttle
that crashed on Earth. I did base his form on Skywarp and he does
posses many of his abilities, so I will not actually close that avenue
if you want to explore it. 

BTW there is a Skywarp that is a recolor of Armada Starscream, which is
where I got the pic for Nightrazor.

Preston
